claim.claim-text:
14. A breast tomography system comprising:
a detector having first and second opposing surfaces and an edge surface, said detector rotatable about a pivot point located proximate an edge of said detector and in a plane in which the detector lies;
a source disposed a predetermined distance from said detector and arranged to emit a signal toward said detector, said source movable along an arc having a radius measured from the same pivot point as said detector such that said source moves about the pivot point and wherein in response to movement of said source and said detector, said source and said detector are adapted to maintain a spatial relationship which allows collection of tomographic data.
